{"tid":1412093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"16名被捕人士下午提堂 控非法集結襲警等罪","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:48.000Z","uid":263175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5f67a0bd858d0c59eabafefb039548ce81e2d55c","tid":1412093,"uid":263175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】16名被捕人士下午提堂 控非法集結襲警等罪<br />\n<br />\n反送中的浪潮由6月初至今維時逾兩個月，警民衝突處處。警方於周六先後在旺角及觀塘等地拘捕多名示威者，其中16人被控以非法集結及襲警等罪，將於下午分別於九龍城裁判法院及觀塘裁判法提堂。<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59898655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59898655&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=2b84701f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59898655&h=935b278f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59898655</a>"}]}